### Single Agent Orchestration Chaining - Demo HTTP Requests
### Use with the VS Code REST Client extension

### =====================================================
### Local Development Endpoints
### =====================================================

@localBaseUrl = http://localhost:7071

### Health Check (Local)
GET {{localBaseUrl}}/api/health

###

### Start the single-agent orchestration (Local)
# @name localOrchestration
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/api/singleagent/run

###

### Check the status of the orchestration (Local)
# Replace with the instance ID from the response above
@localInstanceId = {{localOrchestration.response.body.$.instanceId}}

GET {{localBaseUrl}}/api/singleagent/status/{{localInstanceId}}

###

### =====================================================
### Azure Deployed Endpoints
### Replace <your-function-app-name> with your actual Function App name
### =====================================================

@azureBaseUrl = https://<your-function-app-name>.azurewebsites.net

### Health Check (Azure)
GET {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/health

###

### Start the single-agent orchestration (Azure)
# @name azureOrchestration
POST {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/singleagent/run

###

### Check the status of the orchestration (Azure)
@azureInstanceId = {{azureOrchestration.response.body.$.instanceId}}

GET {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/singleagent/status/{{azureInstanceId}}
